8:
I arrived at the appointed place on
time, and I even wore the outfit they
requested...
26:
So you're here too, Alk. What's going
on?
41:
We wanted you to enjoy the
holidays too, Miss Trine!
43: We've been planning this for a while!
45:
The holidays are over now, aren't
they?
48:
Well, we couldn't party then
because you were working!
51: Did you also know about this, Alk?
55:
Yeah... Sorry, they made me swear
to keep my mouth shut...
60:
I see... I apologize for being such a
humorless woman.
63:
I doubt I will even be able to provide
you with an interesting
conversation...
66:
Don't worry about it! I'm just happy I
can spend time with my queenâ€”I

68:
Here's your present, Teach! We all

75:
Who else would it be for? Come on,
hurry up and open it!
82:
We all thought it would look good on
you.
99: It is a fine ring, isn't it?
102:
Just wait, Miss Trine! Once we're all
amazing adventurers, we'll get you
an even better gift!
104:
Yeah! So... Please continue to guide
us on our journey!
108:
Understood. As long as you are
satisfied with my teachings, I will
continue to impart my knowledge.
However...
111:
Don't expect me to go easy on you,
even though you've made some
progress.
117:
...Thank you all. I don't know when
the last time I felt like this was...
130:
Can you all hear me? It's me,
Lieutenant Trine.
133:
I hope you'll excuse my strange
outfit. I thought you'd all get a kick
out of it.
136:
...I have found new students. They
even call me teacher.
138:
While they differ from subordinates...
they still remind me of you all.
142:
I have not forgotten my duties to
you, nor do I intend to quit my
search... However...
144: I wish to watch these students grow.
145:
As such, I will be taking a short
detour in my quest. In return, I

stories from my adventures.
155:
Yes... I apologize for dragging you
out here.
158: Ha, little late for that, doncha think?
162:
Well, should we head back to
Starview?
166:
Yes... But may we stop by Palpebra
first?
172:
Of course. I'm sure your students are
waiting for you.
